Sometimes the hardest thing to do is come up with a movie idea that will garner attention and captivate an audience. Here are some ways to brainstorm ideas for a movie:

- Analyze your movie preferences
- Put yourself in an unfamiliar situation
- Imagine being 10 years old with superhuman strength, and saving the world
- Take people from your close circle and put them in unfamiliar situations

There are many more ways to brainstorm movie ideas, and brainstorming is a classic creative technique that helps you create a variety of ideas in a short amount of time. Iterating and exploring new ideas can help lead you to your desired movie plot and script.
